These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, manager, engineer
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, purple, blood-red
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, soy-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the chef is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes blood-red##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the manager##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Job         | manager | chef   | engineer   |
| Color   | purple     | orange | blood-red |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | tea    | fanta      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, entrepreneur, journalist
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, pink, emerald
House: wooden, townhouse, cape-cod
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
3. the entrepreneur is the cape-cod house##1
4. the teacher is the townhouse house##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person who likes pink and the journalist##2
6. the journalist is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Job          | entrepreneur  | teacher     | journalist     |
| Color   | pink     | emerald     | black      |
| House   | cape-cod  | townhouse | wooden |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, scooter, motorbike
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, paramedic
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, sprite
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, mauve, chestnut
1. the bartender is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who likes ebony is between the paramedic and the person drinking sprite##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes mauve is the person driving the scooter##1
5. the person who likes ebony is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport          | bike  | motorbike     | scooter     |
| Job           | paramedic | bartender  | doctor   |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | juice    | sprite |
| Color           | chestnut     | ebony | mauve |

