.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
House: cottage, colonial, tower
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, egyptian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, fonseca, cain
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the tower house##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the colonial house and the dutch##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| House     | colonial    | tower  | cottage |
| Nationality     | malaysian   | egyptian | dutch        |
| Cigar   | cain | oliveros     | fonseca      |

