.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, dahlia, iris
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, boat, ship
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, black, apricot
3 different pets are kept: bird, dog, hamster
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the person who likes apricot and the person driving the ship##2
3. the person driving the taxi is the owner of the dog##1
4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower          | iris    | daffodil     | dahlia      |
| Transport         | taxi | boat | ship |
| Color   | apricot  | black       | ebony       |
| Pet           | dog     | bird       | hamster     |

