.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, april, august
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, software-developer, freelancer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, taxi, car
1. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the nurse##1
3. the fan of country is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Birthday          | april | february | august    |
| Job         | software-developer | freelancer      | nurse |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Transport           | bus      | car       | taxi      |

