.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, chinese, thai
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, mah-jongg
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing, skiing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person playing chess is between the thai and the person driving the car##2
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who's sport is volleyball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Nationality          | thai      | chinese   | egyptian |
| Game         | bridge | chess | mah-jongg |
| Sport   | volleyball      | skiing | surfing   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

