.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, western, epic
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, alhambra, tiparillo
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, badminton, climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is between the alhambra-smoker and the person watching epic movies##2
5. the person watching western movies is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Movie-Genre      | spy       | western      | epic      |
| Cigar         | alhambra    | tiparillo | vegafina      |
| Sport           | climbing | parkour     | badminton |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

