.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-9::.
City: paris, colone, new-york
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, zinnia, rose
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who growszinnia and the person who growsrose##2
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| City      | paris      | colone | new-york     |
| Game          | backgammon   | billiard      | mah-jongg     |
| Flower   | rose  | aconite      | zinnia |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi        | bike     |

