2. the australian is between the egyptian and the person drinking 7up##2
3. the person eating artichoke is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person eating mango is the colombian##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
| Beverage       | 7up       | juice       | almond-milk    |
| Nationality         | colombian | australian | egyptian |
| Food       | mango      | artichoke         | raspberry |
| Transport   | roller        | taxi            | scooter  |

