.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, march
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, firefighter, chef
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, amber
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the firefighter and the dancer##2
5. the person who likes amber is on the far left##1
6. the dancer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Birthday      | march     | may | april      |
| Job         | firefighter  | chef       | dancer |
| Color   | amber   | aquamarine         | purple     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

