.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, marigold, amaryllis
The people have 3 different jobs:  firefighter, security-guard, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, march
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, techno, trance
1. the person who growsmarigold is the social-worker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is between the security-guard and the person who's birthday is in october##2
6. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Flower      | aconite | marigold      | amaryllis            |
| Job           | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard |
| Birthday   | october     | march        | february         |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | reggae    | trance        |

