.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, october, september
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, brazilian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, sunflower
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person watching disaster movies and the brazilian##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the brazilian is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the canadian is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Birthday      | october    | september          | november |
| Nationality          | brazilian | japanese           | canadian        |
| Flower           | daisy | sunflower | bellflower         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

