.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, october, march
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, turkish
City: rome, marseilles, new-york
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, siglo, tiparillo
1. the german is between the tiparillo-smoker and the egyptian##2
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the egyptian is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Birthday   | october | may  | march     |
| Nationality   | turkish    | german | egyptian |
| City           | rome        | new-york   | marseilles  |
| Cigar     | tiparillo      | siglo   | vegafina |

