.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, juice
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, thriller
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, airplane, train
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, ritmeester
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person driving the airplane##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage           | water   | juice   | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | sports   | epic     |
| Transport   | airplane     | bike      | train    |
| Cigar           | tiparillo | aristoff | ritmeester    |

