.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, swisher, blend
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, iris
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, japanese
1. the dutch is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
3. the fan of disco is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who growsdaisy##2
4. the fan of reggae is the japanese##1
5. the spanish is between the swisher-smoker and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Cigar      | aristoff | blend     | swisher        |
| Flower         | tulip   | iris | daisy |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Nationality           | japanese           | spanish    | dutch       |

