.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, singing, writing
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, coach, photographer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, blues, folk
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the coach is the fan of electronic##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the photographer is between the fan of folk and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby        | singing      | traveling | writing |
| Job         | coach     | photographer    | bartender        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic          | blues     | folk       |

 